Name: palm date production, conditioned and dried, organic | energy feed, gross | EN15804GD, U
Category: C:Manufacturing/10:Manufacture of food products/103:Processing and preserving of fruit and vegetables/1030:Processing and preserving of fruit and vegetables
Description: The inventory is an extrapolation modeled for Tunisia and is based on field data from one of the main exporter of the Country. Tunisia is the world's largest exporter of Deglet Noor. The conditioning takes place in a plant located in Beni Khalled (in northern tunisia).
